---
title: Za'atar Chicken Bulgur Bowls with Baby Spinach and Chopped Olives
description: Get ready for Middle Eastern-inspired flavours with this healthy chicken bowl. Fluffy bulgur, briny chopped olives, juicy tomatoes and tender spinach make for a filling and delicious dinner, while za'atar spices add toasty, tangy flair.
